<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.227011>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Photo and drawing of male genitalia: (a) Helicoconis tatricus sp. n. (apo—apophysis, app—appendage, epr—ectoproct, hyp—hypandrium, par—paramere, pen—penis, sty—stylus, S 7, S 8, S 9 — sternite 7 - 9), (b) Helicoconis lutea — specimen from NR Rokoš (25 June 2004, Dúbravy, Strážov Mountains, West Slovakia)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/227011/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

